Q3.png","title":"Veal Pilaf","publishedAt":"2018-09-03T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"41 g","fat":"16 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"54 g","calories":"2204 kJ \/ 527 kcal"},"usefulItems":"casserole dish (3-4 l), oven","hintsAndTricks":["Baking time will vary depending on the rice used.","The amount of sauce in the final dish can be adjusted according to personal preference. For a dryer pilaf, at the end of baking in <nobr>step 7,<\/nobr> bake for a further <nobr>10 minutes<\/nobr> at 180°C.","A cast iron pot may also be used instead of a casserole dish, but will take longer to cook. Adjust baking time accordingly until rice is cooked."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 25m","4 portions"]}